95
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:48,020
I've seen him care so much about someone.

96
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:51,909
In the future, please understand Chen,

97
00:05:51,909 --> 00:05:53,390
this emotionally dense man,

98
