126
00:06:52,750 --> 00:06:53,870
Why isn't it urgent?

127
00:06:53,870 --> 00:06:54,909
If you keep delaying,

128
00:06:54,909 --> 00:06:55,830
the Xu family

129
00:06:56,070 --> 00:06:57,800
