195
00:10:11,150 --> 00:10:12,190
Show him around.

196
00:10:12,190 --> 00:10:13,190
Yes, Miss Qin.

197
00:10:15,870 --> 00:10:16,750
You may leave.

198
00:10:16,780 --> 00:10:17,330
Yes.

199
00:10:21,230 --> 00:10:22,470
