230
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:39,970
Take these embroideries as a gift from me.

231
00:11:42,910 --> 00:11:44,070
The ploy of wealthy young men

232
00:11:44,070 --> 00:11:46,030
spending a fortune to entertain a girl

233
00:11:46,030 --> 00:11:47,110
doesn't work on me.

234
00:11:48,350 --> 00:11:48,910
Come.

235
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:53,590
Wrap up all these embroideries

236
00:11:53,590 --> 00:11:55,030
and send them to Gongyang's Mansion.

237
00:11:55,030 --> 00:11:55,680
Remember,

238
00:11:55,910 --> 00:11:57,630
