239
00:11:57,630 --> 00:11:58,550
Yes.

240
00:12:06,620 --> 00:12:07,950
Young Master Gongyang,

241
00:12:07,990 --> 00:12:10,030
I heard that Xu Muchen has been suspended from his duties.

242
00:12:10,030 --> 00:12:10,910
